www.lamick.co.jp/recruit/new_graduates/\">新卒採用</a></li>\r\n\t <li><a class=\"drawer-menu-item\" href=\"https://job.axol.jp/vb/c/lamick/job/search\">キャリア採用</a></li>\r\n\t <li><a class=\"drawer-menu-item\" href=\"https://www.lamick.co.jp/recruit/faq/\">よくある質問</a></li>\r\n\t<li><a class=\"drawer-menu-item\" href=\"/secure/recruit/contact/index.html\">お問い合わせ</a></li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n    </nav>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div id=\"wrapper_inner\">\r\n    <div id=\"contents\"><h2><img src=\"/recruit_img/fringe_benefits/title01.png\" width=\"960\" height=\"30\" alt=\"TRAINING ～研修制度について～\" /></h2>\r\n<div class=\"article\">\r\n<h3>福利厚生</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"table01\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>\n\t\t\t\t施設</th>\n<td>\n\t\t\t\t独身寮、社宅、保養所</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>\n\t\t\t\t制度</th>\n<td>\n\t\t\t\t従業員持株会、財形貯蓄、職場積立NISA、GLTD保険、<br />\n産前産後休暇、育児休暇、介護休暇、雇用延長、内定者向け海外渡航補助</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>\n\t\t\t\tその他</th>\n<td>\n\t\t\t\t団体保険割引、報奨金、社内部活動支援、資格取得支援、浦和レッズプレミアムパートナー</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>\n\t\t\t\t企業年金</th>\n<td>\n\t\t\t\t退職金制度（DB・DC制度）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>\n\t\t\t\t各種保険</th>\n<td>\n\t\t\t\t社会保険（健康保険、厚生年金）<br />\n労働保険（労災保険、雇用保険）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"img_table01\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"寮外観\" src=\"/recruit_img/fringe_benefits/01_exterior.jpg\"></td>\n<td>\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"茶の間\" src=\"/recruit_img/fringe_benefits/02_living_room.jpg\"></td>\n<td>\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"寮室\" src=\"/recruit_img/fringe_benefits/03_room.jpg\"></td>\n<td>\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"浦和レッズロゴ\" src=\"/recruit_img/fringe_benefits/04_urawareds_logo.png\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"article\">\r\n<h3>イベント</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"post\">\r\n<h4>クリスマス</h4>\r\n<p>従業員の家族へ感謝を込めてフラワーギフト</p>\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"img_list01\">\r\n            <li><img src=\"https://www.lamick.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2017/05/img02-3.jpg\" alt=\"クリスマス\" /></li>\r\n                        \t\r\n            </ul>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"post\">\r\n<h4>夏休み企画(家族向け工場見学会) ※適時開催</h4>\r\n<p>\n\tお父さん、お母さんは、どんな仕事してるかな</p>\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"img_list01\">\r\n            <li><img src=\"https://www.lamick.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2017/05/img03-5.jpg\" alt=\"夏休み企画(家族向け工場見学会) ※適時開催\" /></li>\r\n                        <li><img src=\"https://www.lamick.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2017/05/img04-5.jpg\" alt=\"夏休み企画(家族向け工場見学会) ※適時開催\" /></li>            \t\r\n            </ul>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n</div>\r\n  </div><!-- /#contents -->\r\n  </div><!-- /#wrapper_inner -->\r\n</div><!-- /#wrapper -->\r\n<div class=\"toTop\"><a href=\"#top\">ページの先頭へ</a></div>\r\n<div id=\"footer\">\r\n<div id='footer_inner'>\r\n<div class=\"sub_nav\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"contact\"><a href=\"/secure/recruit/contact/index.html\">お問い合わせ</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"info_area\">\r\n<div class=\"logo\"><a href=\"https://www.lamick.co.jp/recruit\"><img src=\"https://www.lamick.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/Recruit/img/logo02.png\" width=\"191\" height=\"24\" alt=\"大成ラミック株式会社\" /></a></div>\r\n<div id=\"copyright\"><img src=\"https://www.lamick.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/Recruit/img/copyright01.png\" width=\"256\" height=\"10\" alt=\"(C) TAISEI LAMICK CO., LTD. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type='text/javascript' src='https://www.lamick.co.jp/recruit/wp-includes/js/wp-embed.min.js?ver=5.2.12'></script>\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n","finalUrl":"https://www.lamick.co.jp/recruit/fringe_benefits/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T22:36:59.728Z"}